metadata.title: QIANRENON 1/4 inch TRS Stereo Y-Splitter Insert Cable, 6.35mm TRS Male to Dual 6.35mm (1/4 inch) Male TS Stereo Breakout Cable Audio Patch Cord, 5 Feet
features: 1/4 inch TRS stereo Y-splitter insert cable is 1.5m/5ft long for easy movement of the adjustable device and consists of a 6.35mm 1/4" TRS male to 2X 6.35mm 1/4" TS male.

The oxygen-free copper tape shielded wire base has strong anti-interference ability, making the sound quality clear and noise-free, and is used in professional stage performances and equipment that needs to be moved.
Compatible with electronic organ/amplifier/speaker/mixer and other equipment, suitable for 6.35mm TRS three-core jack device and 6.35mm TS two-core device connection, two-way transfer.
1/4 stereo to dual 1/4 mono cable, this is a plug-in cable, usually used in audio consoles, two-way transfer, can be stereo to dual mono, can also be used for dual mono to stereo sound.
Compatible with electronic organ/amplifier/speaker/mixer and other equipment, suitable for 6.35mm TRS three-core jack device and 6.35mm TS two-core device connection, two-way transfer.
description: Name: 6.35 stereo pair 6.35 dual stereo y splitter insert cable
Connector: Gold-plated metal connector for high durability
Application: suitable for audio signal transmission between microphones, mixers, power amplifiers, cameras, sound cards, and speakers
Note:This is not a 3.5mm headphone audio cable, so it is not suitable for mobile phones, computers or tablets.
